headline: Investors Are Flocking to the Stock Market’s Discount Rack
summary: As recently as April, Chase Goodman plowed his extra savings into funds linked to stock-market indexes dominated by the world’s biggest technology companies.  No one will ever confuse Medallion for one of the so-called Magnificent Seven tech companies.
